strings: <voice_0x01001211><se_low>Dominico: What on earth took you so long!?
<voice_0x01001212><se_low>Dominico: That pesky wand-waving bimbo has turned up again! I must erect the barrier immediately!

<voice_0x01001213><se_low>Dominico: Did you find ‘The Big Book of Barriers’!?
Don't disappoint me, now!

<voice_0x01001214><se_low>Dominico: What are you playing at!?
There's no time to fool around!
I need that book!

<voice_0x01001215><se_low>Dominico: Yes, yes! This is it!

<voice_0x01001216><se_low>Dominico: Now let me see... Yes, ‘The Final Barrier’!
I must begin at once! You!
Go outside and stall that meddlesome floozy!
<voice_0x01001217><se_low>Dominico: What are you worrying about!? I'll have it done in a flash! Can't you tell a great magician when you see one!?
<voice_0x01001218><se_low>Dominico: Just before you go! Fiery foo and bubbling goo... Behold!
<Cap><hero> is resurrected!!!
Yangus is resurrected!!!
Jessica is resurrected!!!
Angelo is resurrected!!!
The party is fully healed!
<voice_0x01001219><se_low>Dominico: Now that you're in top form, go and stall that wand-waving menace! Every second counts! Go!
<voice_0x0100121A><se_low>Dominico: What are you waiting for!? I told you to go outside and stall that wand-waving slip of a girl immediately!
<voice_0x0100121B><se_low>Dominico: Now go! GO! If you can just buy enough time to get the barrier in place, I'll show her who's boss!
<voice_0x0100121C><se_low>Dominico: What!? Injured!? We can't afford to waste time! Fiery foo and bubbling goo... Behold!
<voice_0x0100121B><se_low>Dominico: Now go! GO! If you can just buy enough time to get the barrier in place, I'll show her who's boss!
